## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of current data, as the sources consulted are primarily from the early 2000s. The ethical and scientific landscape may have evolved since then, and newer studies or technological advancements might not be reflected in this analysis. Additionally, the report focuses on English-language sources, which may not capture the full spectrum of global perspectives on human cloning.